(2313, 1, '2018-04-17 17:01:49', '2018-04-17 17:01:49', '<p class=\"c-paragraph-2\">All the Xbox One accessories you’ve got now (or have got your eye on) work with Xbox One S. No adapters, no hassle. Just play.</p>\r\nPlay console exclusives like Forza Motorsport 7, Crackdown 3, State of Decay 2, and Gears of War 4 plus blockbusters like Madden 18, Middle-earth™: Shadow of War™, and FIFA 18.', 'Xbox One', '<h1 class=\"c-heading-2 f-lean\">Xbox One 1TB Edition</h1>\r\n<p class=\"c-caption-1\"> HDR</p>\r\n<p class=\"c-caption-1\">Xbox One 1 TB console <span class=\"green-c\">I</span> Xbox Wireless controller <span class=\"green-c\">I</span> Xbox One  vertical stand</p>', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'xbox-one', '', '', '2018-04-22 19:54:00', '2018-04-22 19:54:00', '', 0, 'http://localhost/FatherOfGaming/?post_type=product&#038;p=2313', 0, 'product', '', 0),
